    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; 5 Engine Service Manual - Fuel System - Installation - Secondary Fuel
        Filter Assembly
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc id="m8" svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Secondary Fuel Filter Assembly</title>
        <figure id="f3001312" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figj11/j11060.cgm" type="cgm" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="352px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Fuel pressure regulator poppet assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Oil filter assembly</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Secondary fuel filter housing</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Screw, M6 x 25 (3)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Pressure regulator cover gasket</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Viton O-ring, size #115</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Poppet gasket seal</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Brass poppet</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Pressure regulator valve spring</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new pressure regulator cover gasket and new O-ring into the fuel filter housing.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Make sure brass poppet has a new gasket seal on it before placing assembly into fuel filter
                housing. Brass poppet goes in first, spring is oriented toward oil filter side.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install three M6 x 25 screws through the fuel filter housing and into the oil filter
                assembly. Thread screws in evenly, watching the alignment of gasket, O-ring and poppet spring.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten Three M6 x 25 screws to
                <hotlnk document="eges390_208.xml" xrefid="t390000702">special torque</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="t390000702"/>.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
